&lt;a href="https://www.nordicsemi.com/eng/Products/Bluetooth-low-energy/nRF51822" target="_blank">&lt;span class="s2">Nordic Semiconductor&lt;/span> – MCU 제공&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
